to wait for God's timing...

01:27:03.434 --> 01:27:06.847
...and above all,
to be satisfied in Christ,

01:27:06.905 --> 01:27:08.748
whether He brings us
together or not.

01:27:12.810 --> 01:27:16.257
Thank you for being
a true friend.

01:27:16.314 --> 01:27:18.885
Sincerely, Grace.

01:27:27.425 --> 01:27:29.336
