Why don't you go find Grace?

01:28:49.974 --> 01:28:51.214
Can you do that'?

01:28:51.275 --> 01:28:52.618
That'd be good.

01:29:01.352 --> 01:29:03.764
It's beautiful, isn't it'?

01:29:03.821 --> 01:29:05.300
Clint'?!

01:29:05.356 --> 01:29:06.460
